&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/217408/g%c3%bcnter-z%c3%b6chbauer&quot; title=&quot;564,452 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Günter Zöchbauer&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment65311853_36325468&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2016-08-16 16:04:25Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Aug 16, 2016 at 16:04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I am using RC4 and the example was quite useful. Only thing that i wanted to mention is i had to add below code for binding to work properly        this.cmpRef.changeDetectorRef.detectChanges();&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/887701/rajee&quot; title=&quot;252 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Rajee&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment65341450_36325468&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2016-08-17 11:06:41Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Aug 17, 2016 at 11:06&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
